docs {
  ## Get Node Version

  Retrieve the version string of the running beacon node.

  ### Response (200)
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "version": "Lighthouse/v4.5.0-441fc16/x86_64-linux"
    }
  }
  ```
}
